snippet.title: Timelie - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Get your copy now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1150950/Timelie/

Timelie is a cooperative adventure through time, which every precise moment of action is crucial. Use your abilities to solve puzzles and uncover the secrets of this abstract world.

Follow us to know more on
- Official Site: http://www.timeliegame.com
- Timelie Facebook fanpage: https://www.facebook.com/TimelieGame/
- Urnique Studio Twitter: https://twitter.com/UrniqueStudio
- Urnique Studio fanpage: https://www.facebook.com/urniquestudio/

Timelie, an award winning a stealth puzzle game, World champion of Imagine Cup 2016 in Game Category, developed by Urnique Studio. "No Last Eternity" composed by Aun The Voice ft. Natbua. Character design by Dinsai Studio.
